Tom Burke SAPS in Lephalale along with the Heritage Protection Group (HPG) and the SAPS trio crime task force made a breakthrough in the attack and farm murder on the farm Dale in Tom Burke. Two Mozambique suspects have been arrested. One is the driver of the vehicle and the other a farm worker that supplied information.The vehicle used in the attack has been recovered. Four suspects are still at large and the investigation is ongoing. Read the original article in Afrikaans onÂ Waterberg Veiligheid/Sekuriteit